## ðŸ“ƒ Privacy Policy

**Barcodia does not collect, store, or share any personal or sensitive user data.**

- All data entered in the app (e.g., product names, prices, codes) is used only for local label generation and printing.
- No internet connectivity is required or used for processing or storing user input.
- We do not use third-party analytics or advertising SDKs.

If you have any concerns about privacy, please contact us at: **support@barcodia.app**

